Body:
And every human being's destiny have We tied to his
			neck;<span class='fn'>17</span> and on the Day of Resurrection We shall bring
			forth for him a record which he will find wide open;

VERILY, this Qur'an shows the way to all that is most
			upright,<span class='fn'>10</span> and gives the believers who do good deeds the
			glad tiding that theirs will be a great reward;
